    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense but it's still frustrating. so basically, since the interest is based on the total balance, in the first few years, the interest takes up almost the entire payment? is there anything in the math itself that causes this \"slow start\" effect, or is it just how the math works out?",
